info.name: ComplyCube  API V1 - Demo
info.description:
This collection is crafted to give you an overview of the endpoints in a practical, **scenario-driven way**. It is perfect for you to understand the ComplyCube API and see it work quickly.

It uses a **mock** account and will work out of the box without setting up any environment.

item.name: Perform a Standard AML Screening Check

request.description: Create a client so that you can perform checks on.

This will run a Standard AML Screening check on your client.

Insert the **Client ID** in the body below.

This will return the result for the Standard AML Screening Check.

Insert the generated **Check ID**, from the previous request, in the URL below.

**NOTE**: If in the response, the `status` is pending, wait about 10 seconds and try running this request again.

**NOTE**: The check is not real, so the response will always be static.
